title: Whitney Houston Live: Welcome Home Heroes (1991) DVD
description:
Welcome Home Heroes with Whitney Houston, was Whitney Houston's first ever solo televised concert and DVD/video release. The DVD/video presents Houston performing live at the Naval Air Station in Norfolk, Virginia on March 31, 1991. The video was originally released on May 14, 1991, and the DVD was released in 2002. The concert was dedicated to the troops, their families, and military and government dignitaries in honor of those returning from the Gulf War.

This is the Japanese Import version, Lossless DVD rip with menus left out. The best version of this concert out there. Strangely the best full concert recording of Whitney Houston, the best female pop singer that ever lived, exists. Unfortunately it contains burned in Japanese subs, but not that annoying. Forget the Amazon version, go for this free version.

I don't mind if you leave your gratitude in the form of comments/feedback!
